Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • GameObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnyGroup
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bullet, EnemyShip, PlayerShip

    public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements AnyGroup
    A class that encapsulates what every game object has namely: position, velocity, health, life status, image, rotation angle, width and height.
    Author:
    Mossad Helali
